To test the blog run the following command:

hugo server --disableFastRender --renderToMemory

To test it on other devices on the locahost add the bind option, as shown below

hugo server --disableFastRender --renderToMemory --bind=0.0.0.0

To build all html pages into the local output folder, use the command below

HUGO_ENV=production hugo --minify --destination=/tmp/output
